// @test regression/INV067-imported-library-no-false-positive
// @description The imported-library member check must NOT fire on a real library export (ta.dema) nor on a builtin function reached through a colliding library alias (ta.sma - the builtin still resolves alongside the library; TV-confirmed clean 2026-06-19). Members of libraries we do NOT vendor stay lenient too (the #41 residual) - covered by the corpus's many unvendored imports at 0 regressions. See investigations/INV067-imported-library-member-validation/notes.md.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects no-errors
//@version=6
import TradingView/ta/9 as ta
a = ta.dema(close, 10)
b = ta.sma(close, 10)
plot(a + b)
